Horizontal Slides Project

Overview
This project is a simple yet effective HTML and CSS implementation of a three-horizontal-slide presentation. Each slide contains specific content that provides an overview of myself, my skills and knowledge, and my interests for future work and professional growth.

Features
Slide 1: Introduction about myself.
Slide 2: Information about my skills and knowledge.
Slide 3: Details about my interests and aspirations in the corporate world.

How to Use
Clone the repository to your local machine using:

sh
Copy code
git clone https://github.com/Jayeshpansuriya/horizontal-slides-project.git
Open the index.html file in your preferred web browser to view the slides.

Technologies Used
HTML5
CSS3

Project Structure
index.html: Main HTML file containing the structure of the slides.
styles.css: CSS file for styling the slides.

